09:15.970 --> 09:18.929
[cheers and applause]

09:18.929 --> 09:20.669
- Welcome back to "Fool Us,"

09:20.669 --> 09:23.970
where magicians could come at
Penn and Teller from anywhere,

09:23.970 --> 09:26.429
including from
right behind them!

09:26.429 --> 09:27.769
Just kidding.

09:27.769 --> 09:30.799
They'll come out right here
after we watch this.

09:33.700 --> 09:35.070
- My name is Angela Funovits,

09:35.070 --> 09:37.330
and I'm a professional
mentalist.

09:37.330 --> 09:39.070
I grew up as a small town girl.

09:39.070 --> 09:41.370
I had this huge interest
in magic.

09:41.370 --> 09:43.700
My other dream
was to become a doctor,

09:43.700 --> 09:45.769
and I was able to become both.

09:45.769 --> 09:47.370
The nurses
that I work with joke

09:47.370 --> 09:50.769
that the Angela that's onstage
is just my evil twin.

09:50.769 --> 09:53.330
I get to things
that are daring,

09:53.330 --> 09:56.870
that are dangerous,
and I get to lie on purpose

09:56.870 --> 09:58.269
and get away with it.

09:58.269 --> 10:01.629
Medicine can have
some similarities with magic.

10:01.629 --> 10:05.899
Patients come in and they are
very much afraid of the unknown.

10:05.899 --> 10:08.169
One of the most powerful things
that I can do,

10:08.169 --> 10:11.669
is to build and establish
a certain trust with a patient.

10:11.669 --> 10:13.769
It's the same thing
that I have to do onstage.

10:13.769 --> 10:15.929
People have to trust you

10:15.929 --> 10:17.970
before they're gonna let you
fool them.

10:20.230 --> 10:21.970
[cheers and applause]

10:21.970 --> 10:25.929
- This med school graduate
specializes in dermatology,

10:25.929 --> 10:28.570
but can she get underneath
Penn and Teller's skin

10:28.570 --> 10:30.129
with this next trick?

10:30.129 --> 10:33.899
Please welcome Angela Funovits.

10:33.899 --> 10:36.899
[cheers and applause]

10:39.269 --> 10:41.500
- Thank you very much.

10:41.500 --> 10:44.330
Throughout the ages, there have
been countless demonstrations

10:44.330 --> 10:47.169
of subliminal
and subconscious influence

10:47.169 --> 10:49.370
that have proven to be
nothing but a hoax.

10:49.370 --> 10:52.700
However, dozens of studies
have shown

10:52.700 --> 10:55.600
that human behavior
can be primed in various ways.

10:55.600 --> 10:58.070
With that idea in mind...

10:58.070 --> 11:00.500
we're going to play a game.

11:00.500 --> 11:03.929
I'm going to use
this here paper ball

11:03.929 --> 11:07.399
to select one random
audience member

11:07.399 --> 11:11.830
to act as a test subject
of sorts.

11:11.830 --> 11:13.830
Please catch.

11:15.029 --> 11:16.529
You, sir.

11:16.529 --> 11:18.230
You'll make a perfect
test subject.

11:18.230 --> 11:19.730
What is your name, sir?
- Jason.

11:19.730 --> 11:20.870
- Jason.

11:20.870 --> 11:23.129
I'm going to be showing you
a series

11:23.129 --> 11:27.100
of several images,
each with a word association.

11:27.100 --> 11:30.230
So, starting off.

11:30.230 --> 11:33.230
Love.

11:33.230 --> 11:35.330
Danger.

11:35.330 --> 11:37.600
Fire.

11:37.600 --> 11:39.870
Chance.

11:39.870 --> 11:42.370
Poison.

11:42.370 --> 11:44.600
Having seen those,

11:44.600 --> 11:47.730
I'd like you now to take a look
at this blank slate,

11:47.730 --> 11:52.230
and form in your mind any word
in the English language.

11:52.230 --> 11:54.100
Do you have one in mind?
- Yes.

11:54.100 --> 11:56.700
- Go ahead and say that word
for us out loud, please.

11:56.700 --> 11:58.600
- Gold.
- Gold.

11:58.600 --> 12:00.370
- G-O-L-D?
- Yes.

12:00.370 --> 12:02.000
- Gold.

12:02.000 --> 12:04.970
And...sir,

12:04.970 --> 12:06.629
before we go any further,

12:06.629 --> 12:08.299
I must say.

12:08.299 --> 12:10.500
Some people might wonder,

12:10.500 --> 12:14.169
is it possible for me to have
influenced his decision?

12:14.169 --> 12:17.600
And to say that I somehow made
you choose the word "gold"

12:17.600 --> 12:20.399
with anything I have just done
is completely ridiculous.

12:20.399 --> 12:25.500
But you haven't seen
what's inside that box.

12:25.500 --> 12:27.500
You still have
that paper ball in hand?

12:27.500 --> 12:30.269
Please bring it on up here
and join me.

12:30.269 --> 12:32.470
Give him a big round
of applause.

12:32.470 --> 12:34.769
[cheers and applause]

12:34.769 --> 12:37.200
Thank you.
- You're welcome.

12:37.200 --> 12:38.429
- Nice to meet you.
- Nice to meet you again.

12:38.429 --> 12:39.730
- So like I said,

12:39.730 --> 12:41.799
we need to get
to what's inside of this box.

12:41.799 --> 12:43.070
We'll leave that there.

12:43.070 --> 12:45.529
What I brought for you...

12:45.529 --> 12:46.799
as you can see,

12:46.799 --> 12:48.799
is an American English
dictionary.

12:48.799 --> 12:50.330
Now come right on over here.
- Okay.

12:50.330 --> 12:52.629
- You and I are gonna stand
right here

12:52.629 --> 12:54.529
and we're gonna look up
your word: "gold."

12:54.529 --> 12:57.230
That's your responsibility
right now. Go ahead.

12:57.230 --> 12:59.370
- I'll do my best.
- All right.

12:59.370 --> 13:02.269
So let's see...
We're at "gaffe."

13:02.269 --> 13:04.230
"Geometry."

13:04.230 --> 13:06.830
Getting there...
- Mm-hmm.

13:08.000 --> 13:11.200
- "Gossipy," oh.
Wait a second.

13:11.200 --> 13:12.669
What do we have here?

13:12.669 --> 13:18.500
We have page 210 on the left,
page 213 on the right...

13:18.500 --> 13:20.330
You've almost found your word,
correct?

13:20.330 --> 13:21.399
- Almost.

13:21.399 --> 13:23.730
- Go ahead and show that
there...

13:23.730 --> 13:27.000
is that one page

13:27.000 --> 13:29.769
ripped out of the center.

13:29.769 --> 13:33.629
Right about where your word
"gold" should have been.

13:33.629 --> 13:36.269
And the question is,

13:36.269 --> 13:38.129
where's the page?

13:38.129 --> 13:40.330
You'll remember when I came
out here, I started off

13:40.330 --> 13:42.070
with a little paper ball.

13:42.070 --> 13:46.029
I tossed that paper ball out
to randomly select you.

13:46.029 --> 13:48.700
Please hold this open
just like this...

13:50.230 --> 13:53.429
because this right here,

13:53.429 --> 13:56.299
in play the entire time...

13:59.629 --> 14:02.169
Is that your word?

14:02.169 --> 14:04.269
- That's gold.
[cheers and applause]

14:04.269 --> 14:07.230
Wow.
- A perfect match.

14:08.769 --> 14:11.399
Thank you, everybody.
Thank you, Jason.

14:11.399 --> 14:14.600
- Funovits,
ladies and gentlemen!

14:14.600 --> 14:17.029
That was incredible!
- Thank you.

14:17.029 --> 14:18.899
- Wow.

14:18.899 --> 14:23.299
So, med school and magician.

14:23.299 --> 14:25.799
- And magician, yes.
- And you sort of always,

14:25.799 --> 14:28.230
even as a child,
had both in mind?

14:28.230 --> 14:29.570
